<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/21854971-susan-reeves-demasi"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1372811956i/21854971._UY100_CR25,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/21854971-susan-reeves-demasi">Susan Reeves deMasi</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Somebody saw the twins through the window. They called Child Services, who sent people to take the kids away. Myra went nuts (well, MORE nuts) because<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Somebody saw the twins through the window. They called Child Services, who sent people to take the kids away. Myra went nuts (well, MORE nuts) because they were taking her children, so they carted her off to the institution.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
